For me, a part of that section is the researchers need to find some reason that this SCP keeps popping up again and again, despite not having any other anomalous properties. The research team figures there has to be some odd compulsory or movement ability of the menu, having a hard time believing that normal people would continue to use a blatantly supernatural object that produces meat that tastes unusual. So, they explicitly test for commonly known SCP abilities, and time and time again find the menu to be completely mundane aside from its delivery ability.







