01 Oct 2011 17:03






It can however move species up in the severity list (from vulnerable, to endangered, to critically endangered etc.), and it can certainly cause extinction.

A lot of the species it uses for meat are on the declining end of that species existence - without the menu's influence, several would probably be in the recovery stages.

So yeah, it won't put a species on the list, but it will definitely keep them there.





